## 9. AUTHORITATIVE CONTROL MATRIX

These controls are NON-NEGOTIABLE. Every relevant screen must enforce them exactly as specified. HARD = system blocks. AUTO = system enforces automatically. SOFT = warning only.

### Labour Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| L-01 | Mechanic must be clocked on to perform work | HARD |
| L-02 | Mechanic can only have ONE active job at any time | HARD |
| L-03 | Clocking off auto-pauses any active job | AUTO |
| L-04 | Time entries are immutable after job closure | HARD |
| L-05 | Time entries are immutable after invoicing | HARD |

### Safety Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| S-01 | Mandatory safety & readiness checklist before diagnosis | HARD |
| S-02 | Safe work environment confirmation required | HARD |
| S-03 | Confirmation that mechanic is not blocking a faster job | HARD |
| S-04 | VIN entry mandatory before diagnosis can begin | HARD |
| S-05 | Walk-around video or photos (vehicle condition before work) mandatory before safety checklist can be completed | HARD |

### Diagnosis & Evidence Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| D-01 | Diagnosis required before repair can begin | HARD |
| D-02 | Defects must be logged before job can continue | HARD |
| D-03 | Defect evidence (photo or video) is mandatory per defect | HARD |
| D-04 | Defect severity (Red = safety / Orange = non-safety) mandatory | HARD |

### Quality Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| Q-01 | Mandatory test / test-drive confirmation | HARD |
| Q-02 | Mechanic clean-down checklist mandatory | HARD |
| Q-03 | Tools & equipment return confirmation | HARD |
| Q-04 | Job notes required (voice or text) | HARD |

### Approval Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| A-01 | Two-hand-touch manager approval required before job closes | HARD |
| A-02 | Manager disclaimer auto-inserted (name + vehicle ID auto-filled) | AUTO |
| A-03 | Mechanic CANNOT finalise job without manager approval | HARD |
| A-04 | OPS close-out mandatory | HARD |
| A-05 | OPS close-out second timer enforced | AUTO |

### Commercial Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| C-01 | PO / customer approval required before any work commences | HARD |
| C-02 | Job cannot be assigned or started without a PO | HARD |
| C-03 | Extra work requires explicit customer approval | HARD |
| C-04 | Approved extra work must be created as a NEW job | HARD |
| C-05 | Job is the sole commercial billing unit | AUTO |

### Billing Controls
| ID | Rule | Gate |
|---|---|---|
| B-01 | Job cannot be invoiced without approvals | HARD |
| B-02 | Cash sale must be paid before vehicle release | HARD |
| B-03 | Account jobs must be invoiced before vehicle release | HARD |
| B-04 | Vehicle cannot be released without confirmation | HARD |
| B-05 | Invoices are job-based only (never vehicle-based) | AUTO |

